                                    <font key="font" metaFont="smallSystem"/>
                                    <string key="title">This application comes with a Finder extension that allows you to create an icon set directly in the Finder by right-clicking an application or an image file. By default, the extension uses the settings made in the Icons application. So it applies the default banner, uses the selected output size and animation duration, and creates only the icon types selected in the application.

